Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
On November 11, 2009, Applied Materials, Inc. ("Applied" or "the Company") announced its financial results for its fiscal year and fourth quarter ended October 25, 2009. A copy of Applied's press release is furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1. A copy of the transcript of the conference call relating to the financial results for these periods and the presentation accompanying the call are attached hereto as Exhibits 99.2 and 99.3, respectively.
