          other than to another Acquired Corporation, none of the Acquired Corporations has sold, issued or granted, or authorized the issuance of: (i) any capital stock or other security (except for Company Common Stock issued upon the valid exercise of outstanding Company Equity Awards and except for sales, issuances or grants to newly hired employees of an Acquired Corporation); (ii) any option, warrant or right to acquire any capital stock or any other security (except for Company Equity Awards identified in Part 2.3(b) of the Disclosure Schedule); or (iii) any instrument convertible into or exchangeable for any capital stock or other security;
