th
day (or, if such day is not a Business Day, the first Business Day thereafter) following earlier to occur of (i), in the case of redemption pursuant to clause (b)(i) above, May 31, 2012, or (ii), in the case of redemption pursuant to clause (b)(ii) above, the date the Merger Agreement is terminated (the "").
